      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. For the lesson, I also want to make sure the students understand why this is so important. Could you add a section explaining why some people argue that using \"substantive due process\" this way is actually a dangerous way for judges to bypass the democratic process and override the will of the people?",
